results.name: Wheat
results.title: Timberland 6" Premium Waterproof Boot Wheat
results.description:
The Timberland 6 Inch Premium Waterproof Wheat is one of the variants from the Timberland brand, a common footwear among men and trekking sports enthusiasts.

The boot is made from leather material at the upper part and rubber at the sole. The design unleashes in style code TB010062-713. 90% of the upper part of Timberland Waterproof is wheat, while the collar is black. The design consists of a stylish suede with a Timberland logo branded on the side of the shoe.

Timberland 6 Inch Premium Waterproof Wheat was first released on June 1, 2019, at a retail price of $210.

results.name: Black Nubuck Premium
results.title: Timberland 6" Boot Black Nubuck Premium
results.description:
The Timberland 6-Inch Black Nubuck features a black Nubuck leather construction which comes from top-grain calfskin or cowhide. The leather is layered on the collar to create comfort and protect the feet from outside elements. Timberland also includes anti-fatigue technology that absorbs sudden impact and returns that energy to where it came from.

The Timberland 6-Inch Black Nubuck released in January of 2018 and retailed for $190.

results.title: Timberland 6" Boot Wheat (GS)
results.description: The Timberland 6 Wheat GS is a classic boot that has been updated with modern materials and construction techniques. The upper is made from premium nubuck leather that is both durable and comfortable. The boot is also waterproof, making it perfect for outdoor activities. The wheat colorway is a timeless look that will never go out of style. The release date for this boot was January 1st, 2018, and it retails for $130. The Timberland 6 Wheat GS is a versatile boot that can be worn with a variety of outfits, from jeans to khakis. It is a must-have for anyone who wants a durable and stylish boot that can handle any weather conditions.

results.name: Beef and Broccoli
results.title: Timberland 6" Field Boot Beef and Broccoli
results.description:
The Timberland 6'' Field Boot Beef and Broccoli is a reimagination of the original Timberland 6 Field Boot that was first released in 1983. It is a shoe that is designed for being both a classic work boot and the footwear of choice for hikers.

This Timberland 6'' Field Boot model is a high top style that has a dark brown body with black and green overlays. The sole of the shoe is made out of strong rubber, while the body is primarily composed of waterproof leather. The laces are stretchy and designed to help provide ultimate support.

A feature of the Timberland 6'' Field Boot Beef and Broccoli that our team of experts particularly enjoys is the direct-inject polyurethane outsoles that help to provide durability and support to the wearer. This Timberland model was first made available for sale in January of 2017 and had a retail price that started at $175.

results.name: Black (GS)
results.title: Timberland 6" Premium Boot Black (GS)
results.description:
The Timberland 6" Premium Boot Black (GS) is a grade school-sized Timberland 6" Premium Boot in a monochromatic black colorway.

This Timberland boot features a premium full-grain waterproof leather upper with a padded collar covered in soft leather. Primaloft lining keeps the feet warm and comfortable. Other details include a lace closure system with matching metallic eyelets and Taslan fiber laces, the signature Timberland branding etched at the lateral heel, waterproof seam-sealed construction, and matching stitching. Finishing off the design is a black sole unit with a rubber lug outsole for traction.

What our experts particularly love about this grade school-sized Timberland boot is its simple colorway and premium construction. The upper materials contribute to its comfort and durability, while the simple colorway gives it a timeless and versatile aesthetic appeal, making it a standout choice for outdoor and everyday wear. The Timberland 6" Premium Boot Black (GS) was made available on January 1st, 2018. Initially, it retailed at $130.

results.name: Wheat (TD)
results.title: Timberland 6" Premium Boot Wheat (TD)
results.description:
The Timberland 6" Premium Boot Wheat (TD) takes Timberlands signature 6" Premium Boot silhouette and applies it to a toddler-sized model in a warm Wheat colorway.

Like the adult-sized variation, this work boot boasts an upper made of soft nubuck leather treated with a water-repellent solution. In addition, the boots seam-sealed construction prevents water from seeping into the shoe and adds a smooth finish where the nubuck panels overlap. The durable rubber outsole features a texturized lug design that grips the ground and contributes to the shoes recognizable silhouette. To further Timberlands sustainability goals, 10 percent of the outsole is constructed from plant-based materials instead of ones that use petroleum.

Our experts like the way the PrimaLoft insulation keeps the foot warm without adding bulky padding, perfect for winter play days. The toddler-sized Timberland 6" Premium Boot Wheat (TD) was released on January 4, 2019, and retailed at $90.

results.name: Wheat (Women's)
results.title: Timberland 6" Premium Waterproof Boot Wheat (Women's)
results.description:
The Timberland 6" Premium Waterproof Boot Wheat (Women's) is inspired by the original Timberland waterproof boot. With a work boot aesthetic, this rugged but stylish footwear offers fashionable function in any weather. This shoe has been specifically sized for women.

This waterproof boot features a shaft height of 5.25 inches, and the upper is crafted from premium Timberland leather in a wheat-colored hue. Rope laces thread through metal eyelets up to the padded collar of black leather. The lining is leather and the anti-fatigue footbed is removable. A Timberland logo is branded on the lateral heel, giving this shoe its rightful distinction. The gum rubber outsole is deeply lugged for traction.

Our favorite aspect of this women's shoe is the 200 grams of PrimaLoft insulation that will keep your feet warm in the nastiest of conditions. The Timberland 6" Premium Waterproof Boot Wheat (Women's) was released on January 12, 2023, for $170 retail.

results.name: Hazel Highway
results.title: Timberland 40 Below Super Boot Hazel Highway
results.description:
The Timberland 40 Below Superboot Brown was originally designed for the harsh Alaskan climate, but the classic boot has been available for all terrains.

The 40 Below Superboot in Brown measures about 9 inches and includes an exclusive tannage Hazel Highway leather inspired by the Krymp Oxide leather of the original 1979 model. The shoe also comes with waterproof seam-sealed construction, anti-slip D-ring hardware, and a triple-bubble collar. The whole design by Timberland is rounded off by a black Vibram Ecostep sole crafted from 30% recycled rubber.

The Timberland 40 Below Superboot Brown was first released on the 1st of January 2018 for an original price of $260.

results.name: Veneda Carter Wheat
results.title: Timberland 6" Boot Veneda Carter Wheat
results.description:
The Timberland 6" Boot Veneda Carter Wheat is a special-edition 6" Boot from Timberland that was designed in collaboration with renowned stylist Veneda Carter.

The iconic yellow Timberland boot got a new image with this collaboration model that stays true to the original in some aspects, while some parts get the Veneda Carter make over. This iteration is the wheat patent leather colorway. It features a glossy patent leather upper in a sumptuous wheat color. The Timberland logo sits near the lateral ankle. Inside the boot there is ReBOTL lining, which is an eco-friendly material. The eyelets are silver metallic and lace up the two-toned rope laces. Underfoot is a durable outsole.

Our experts think that the waterproof, shiny patent leather upper keeps feet protected and dry and is what sets the Timberland 6" Boot Veneda Carter Wheat apart from other boots out there. It was released on March 5, 2024, with a retail list price of $250.
